strings.Value: "How does it feel to be chieftain?"
"Greetings. I'm glad you found time to visit your {d|c41 Chief Ashman}allies{/d}."
"I have some experience leading people. Before the tribe split, I used to command armies that were bigger than the whole tribe is now."

"{g|Gorum}Gorum{/g} doesn't grant us glorious fights these days. We use this time to restore our strength before the next war breaks out. As I'm sure you're aware, there's nothing more fleeting than a period of peace."
"I knew you weren't to be trusted!"
